{
  "chapter": 20,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十回　祥麟公子。剑客行故事继续。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "惭愧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老前辈！你说呀！他们是谁？叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老前辈！你快说出他们叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个是镇江的霸王鞭樊非。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "武林四公子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "武林四公子的父亲……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凌风公子之父，摘星手慕容涵？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "安乐公子之父，乾坤掌云宗龙？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "端方公于之父，混元指司空晋？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哎呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "命门",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是一个叫雷大叔的人送给我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈在黑暗中用手摸的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "用手摸书",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "噢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老前辈认识？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么不认识！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老前辈是何人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老前辈，怎么知道晚辈杀父的仇人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神驴铁胆！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是他老人家！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他老人家虽然游踪无定。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死人居",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小恩公……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死人居",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秋老虎",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叭！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小乔初嫁，雄姿英发",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小朋友！不应该无故打人，打到我没有什么关系，若是脾气坏的人，一定不会饶过你们……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "噗哧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "的一声，不偏不倚，正打在乌龟头上，把那乌龟打了一个翻身，真正是",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘻！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兰兰，不许淘气……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "噗通",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有什么新奇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老先生是叫我吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哎！真乃顽冥不灵！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你",
      "tone": "陈述",
